synopsis: The tensions rise between the bass player and the singer of a metal band both on and off stage.
If the pizza delivery boy delivers a pizza to the Arctic circle in 5 minutes or less he will get a big tip, or so he thinks.

synopsis: The story of a lonely young man as he inexplicably wakes up in his dark and empty apartment one day. What follows is his journey through this mysterious and unrecognizable world he is thrown into. As he tries to grasp the surreal occurrences happening around him, he comes closer to unraveling the truth behind his existence and his dark past.
